                <p class="fw-lighter">Users can rate and review other members based on successful exchanges to build trust in the platform.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4 col-12 feature p-4 text-center">
                <img class="icon-img w-25" src="~/Images/security.png" alt="Review & Rating System" />
